        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You call upon your patron's power to better uncover secrets.</p>\n<p>When you Cast the Spell, the target can @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Recall Knowledge (Lore)]{Recall Knowledge}, @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Seek]{Seek}, or @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Sense Motive]{Sense Motive}. The target gains a +1 status bonus to the skill or Perception used for the roll, and this bonus remains as long as you @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Sustain a Spell]{Sustain the Spell}.</p>\n<p>The target is temporarily immune to discern secrets for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (5th)</strong> You can target two creatures instead of one.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Recall Knowledge)]{Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Recall Knowledge)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Seek)]{Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Seek)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Sense Motive)]{Spell Effect: Discern Secrets (Sense Motive)}</p>"
